info.name: Vellenum API
info.description: Postman v2.1 collection for Vellenum API. Set {{base_url}} and {{token}} environment variables before use.

request.description: Restaurant-specific registration (seller_category_id=1). Required user fields + restaurant fields. File fields represented as placeholder IDs or filenames.
Login and receive access token. Token goes into Authorization header as: Bearer {{token}}
Request an OTP for verification or password reset (dev returns OTP in response).
Revoke current user's token (requires Authorization header).
Downloads file binary from storage if present.
